islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:35:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a01bfc696e93e7e80e14aa9d759475ff7d628b3","tid":1424960,"uid":172284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:41:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"034fbd95257402faf4ee4ce5731dd2844f6b3001","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:07:41.000Z","msg":"網上見到<br />\n<br />\n懇請分享出去，希望唔好破壞交通燈😟，交通燈聲音對於我哋睇唔到嘅朋友係相當相當之緊要，一般人判斷覺得安全情況下見到冇車照過馬路<br />\n或者兜路 搵天橋代替😉<br />\n但係我哋睇唔到嘅朋友，通常只會揀一條自己最熟悉嘅路去行，交通燈失靈冇聲音，我哋就唔敢過馬路啦，未必知道附近有乜嘢路可以代替，交通燈聲音除咗協助我哋安全過馬路之外，最重要係可以幫我地定位大約知道自己身處喺邊一度🥺眼睛唔方便真係有苦自己知😢大家繼續加油，我睇唔到，心仍然同大家一齊嘅，比胡椒噴霧噴到眼睛一樣會痛一樣會流眼水，我同大家嘅血顏色係一樣嘅🙌"},{"pid":"8f8a8168aa6b844e5123d2a3a184b9376cc19483","tid":1424960,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:24:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1554c5dc0b5e6dac19b5fd8a9e08cd9476c2f14","tid":1424960,"uid":56274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15464fbad9098193e51833ad6e0b73033d460f28","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:53:23.000Z","msg":"絕不割蓆!!!<br />\n<br />\n核爆都不割蓆，但我地比林奠叻既係我地會聽民意反省同改進!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dynRjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dynRjS</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:27:31.000Z","msg":"錫你春袋割唔割！"},{"pid":"4ec5c85fe4435996b16269e72c692b521098df22","tid":1424960,"uid":160075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:30:09.000Z","msg":"推 呢位絲打真係幾有道理    所以我都求下各位手足睇完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c900c2deb6625436ac149a32aec6e528f0e23431","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:31:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">絕不割蓆!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果我地割蓆，排除唔同路既人，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地同林鄭有乜分別？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n明顯對家策略有明顯轉左。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">之前：</span></strong>乜都唔做，等你地黎，後生全贏。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">現在：</span></strong>定性呢場運動唔係「反送中」，係「港獨」。每區（由北角開始，跟住石硤尾，大圍等）由當地有勢力人士牽頭）逐場擊破<br />\n<br />\n要改變策略，要帶返個運動去返原本５大要求。唔係圍警署。<br />\n<br />\n睇下各巴打點睇，點follow"},{"pid":"7d63485be7a34c91998091a5c02a95ea0ce6cd3f","tid":1424960,"uid":27719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:31:52.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f45b7f437ae6a18653ee26c76ffc769e19a0173","tid":1424960,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:32:57.000Z","msg":"多謝分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3565a5385f19215bb193fbb1b9887784b1c76411","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:34:47.000Z","msg":"尋日我地冇人去北角，等佢地食西北風，我地做對左。<br />\n<br />\n依家淨返，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">８月１１日港島東</span></strong>，我地一定唔可以行差踏錯，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">運動一路行落去，出錯失敗既機會愈大</span></span></strong>，所以要想清楚點做。<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位點睇先。"},{"pid":"804f105f3bda2b78a82b162fe6d0529e113da1f0","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:36:30.000Z","msg":"仲有問返自己。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你個初心係乜？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">５大訴求</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n運動定位要緊守，唔好轉左方向。<br />\n我地贏頭段係因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民心支持，群眾路線正確</span></strong>，唔係燒警署。"},{"pid":"313c12e6cbb689f166edff6c78abc98c6ae93b8c","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:53:29.000Z","msg":"回應返樓主個message：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不合作運動: </span></strong>要對返工既人客氣有禮，佢地或者會被感動，但係粗聲粗氣一定唔work,反而失民心（大忌）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工：</span></strong>唔可以成日攪，７７７尋日個記招就係拎番出黎想我地群眾鬥群眾，要等時機同埋真係有topic <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武: </span></strong>佢係我地既皇牌，就因為佢地愈來愈重要，所以常用數一定要減少，可以保留實力，避免送頭，仲有俾時間佢地去唔同地方踩線搵新野。（有傳話佢地目標係８月底前捉最少７００個）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">集會/遊行：</span></strong>依家開始要小心，鬼肯定會多，同埋鄉事派同其他界別用返１４年雨革一樣（如的士佬，小巴佬等）黎打散我地，呢度要盡快踱對策。<br />\n<br />\n上面俾左Ｄ建議，望拋磚引玉。"},{"pid":"258c3c6c19c3074d4dcdd51112b32e71a9f9ba4b","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5453197bb53e4a3a2df0946554a589336695d11","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fedd4027187e9f0a4f19470c1e4d0634a964b8b8","tid":1424960,"uid":298802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0066ae45e9f647d134ba2a801a1423a637f4e2e1","tid":1424960,"uid":298802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:32:36.000Z","msg":"搵時間討論下點贏區選 最少要贏超過六成議席"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"因為要陪養莊腳 迎接出年立法會選舉<br />\n只要立法會超過四十席 到時真的可以光復香港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:57:48.000Z","msg":"係，建制已經做緊野，但甦醒的香港人都唔想投俾政棍<br />\n我地又掛住打狗，冇時間精力討論<br />\n但有功能組別就冇可能超過四十席"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:56:15.000Z","msg":"要睇下文宣個邊有冇計，<br />\n又或者真係要搵Ｄ有選舉經驗既團體，睇下可唔可以協調一下出選，避免鬼打鬼。"},{"pid":"699384556603698b8bf33c53d726b07eb0c58a43","tid":1424960,"uid":115037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:30:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b115dd3ba0f424470a72a086ad1d12303e51fd38","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:34:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b62476f455f2a989cada858433a99b06cf41913","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s