42.000Z","msg":"高汁po<br />\n推推推"},{"pid":"6911a2782bb0096ecdad84ae83467d0246bf843a","tid":1424960,"uid":22854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"認同，堅持者勝"},{"pid":"5f5436492a32b6731b27f0aeb77bd4747438ba41","tid":1424960,"uid":37990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:32:14.000Z","msg":"塞車要有時段，而唔係全日 仲要大家係講到明!!!<br />\n<br />\n勇武e排be water 好叻叻,不過我相信仲有班和班非冇gear既朋友仔唔小心被捕<br />\n唔該,唔齊gear 唔好太前,仲要留多小小位比前線走,因為速龍真係好快"},{"pid":"5b40c239f24fb46e6ecc5f168216d227060203e1","tid":1424960,"uid":301182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:48:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n支持聚焦組織長期三罷，唔好中計俾對家分化"},{"pid":"5a5ff2f444ae437355b83804d716ef0e45ddbb8b","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3565a5385f19215bb193fbb1b9887784b1c76411","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:34:47.000Z","msg":"尋日我地冇人去北角，等佢地食西北風，我地做對左。<br />\n<br />\n依家淨返，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">８月１１日港島東</span></strong>，我地一定唔可以行差踏錯，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">運動一路行落去，出錯失敗既機會愈大</span></span></strong>，所以要想清楚點做。<br />\n<br />\n想問下各位點睇先。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:31:37.000Z","msg":"戰爭勝出一方往往係<span style=\"color: red;\">最少出錯</span>既一方<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係話唔可以錯，而係最緊要會反省同改進!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"3a4d0c3c1e72163e7ff1398bc999ab0f30a0b8da","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"804f105f3bda2b78a82b162fe6d0529e113da1f0","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:36:30.000Z","msg":"仲有問返自己。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你個初心係乜？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">５大訴求</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n運動定位要緊守，唔好轉左方向。<br />\n我地贏頭段係因為<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民心支持，群眾路線正確</span></strong>，唔係燒警署。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:33:23.000Z","msg":"冇錯，堅守五大訴求，鞏固民心"},{"pid":"236af513f283c5b8cfdfaa6d2d8946831467c9f6","tid":1424960,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"034fbd95257402faf4ee4ce5731dd2844f6b3001","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:07:41.000Z","msg":"網上見到<br />\n<br />\n懇請分享出去，希望唔好破壞交通燈😟，交通燈聲音對於我哋睇唔到嘅朋友係相當相當之緊要，一般人判斷覺得安全情況下見到冇車照過馬路<br />\n或者兜路 搵天橋代替😉<br />\n但係我哋睇唔到嘅朋友，通常只會揀一條自己最熟悉嘅路去行，交通燈失靈冇聲音，我哋就唔敢過馬路啦，未必知道附近有乜嘢路可以代替，交通燈聲音除咗協助我哋安全過馬路之外，最重要係可以幫我地定位大約知道自己身處喺邊一度🥺眼睛唔方便真係有苦自己知😢大家繼續加油，我睇唔到，心仍然同大家一齊嘅，比胡椒噴霧噴到眼睛一樣會痛一樣會流眼水，我同大家嘅血顏色係一樣嘅🙌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4964c0ca46d55bfd52c6194268d96efa8dea6bc2","tid":1424960,"uid":300852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:42:06.000Z","msg":"影響政府 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbcb07f541b4fa6c046bcc938481b525c6521279","tid":1424960,"uid":276807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06eb46184ca77a583a9137793e01842327d52636","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:53:13.000Z","msg":"文長，但跪求睇完<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下建議開放討論<br />\n<br />\n1. 關於不合作運動<br />\n要理解<span style=\"color: red;\">有部分工作係唔可以被罷工</span>。例如救護、消防、記者等，佢地堅守崗位先可以保護市民。<br />\n同時亦要<span style=\"color: red;\">理解有部分人真係唔係話罷就罷到</span>，有唔少人真係手停口停/一人養起一頭家(呢個亦係深層次社會問題)，當朝落街有個阿叔眼紅紅話對唔住，佢次次遊行都出黎，但佢為左老婆仔女真係唔可以冇左份工&hellip;&hellip; 即使佢地支持運動，但講到經濟真係無能為力，亦冇任何工會俾到保障佢地，我地要為佢地爭取一個即使罷工都可以有最低保障既社會，唔係逼佢地罷工!!! 當然都希望佢地以其他方式響應，例如黑衣工作/白絲帶之類。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民主係保障每個人都有表達意見既權利!!! 我地唔可以騎劫他人意願，只有由心而 <br />\n發既行動先有最大力量!!! 被逼既只會累積怨氣。</span><br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\na) 塞車要有時段，而唔係全日，遲番工會最大影響係商家/政府，諗下鋪頭開得半日，人工同租又要照俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nb) 同理，道路要留條生路，行得到又唔行得快先最攞命，安全車速/迴旋處練車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nc) 真心唔好搞交通燈，後續影響太大，不合作運動結束後都仲會繼續影響人，日後有咩意外會俾人入，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以令市民因為我地而受傷(底線!!!)</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 關於罷工&amp;罷工集會<br />\n係一定要搞，但係咪繼續分區? 要做到<span style=\"color: red;\">有凝聚力同新聞價值</span>，唔係話J人數，但8.05所見根本冇人討論有幾多人罷工，俾唔到實際輿論壓力，開P日日都可以，但齊心罷工就唔係咁容易，有和理非話下左好大決心罷工，但見唔到有咩用<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\na) 集中集會，而且要有內容，可能係講座/論壇/活動，否則出席只係玩住電話叫下口號，亦多個平台俾市民表達意見，而唔止係網上，其實好多人冇連登/fb/tg(尤其中年同老人家，呢個係時代革命，要連結唔同世代一齊改變呢個社會)<br />\nb) 集會前最少兩個鐘交通暢通，唔少人罷左工但冇交通去集會，變左落街消費/留係屋企。集會人數同遊行人數一樣重要，我知政府唔睇，但商家睇，世界睇，我地自己都睇(支持的力量=堅持落去既力量) <br />\nc) 如果俾到行業罷工人數就更好，一方面俾到實際壓力政府，另一方面俾番credit罷工既手足，認同感其實好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 關於勇武<br />\n都係個句，核爆都不割蓆!!!<br />\n但林奠宜家明顯係想抗爭者同警察對立，辣㷫抗爭者武力升級，只要有一個警察死，佢就明正言順攞哂民意武力清場，和理非亦會收聲，所有義士都會被清算，呢個結果仲衰過出老解!!! 但抗爭者死，佢係絕對唔介意!!! <span style=\"color: green;\">我地絕對唔可以再失去同伴!!! 一個都絕不能再少!!!</span> 我知黑警有幾可恨!!! 但引用天琦係獄中俾我地既信: &quot;<span style=\"color: green;\">不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，仍要時刻保持警覺與思考。</span>&quot; 請三思!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\na) 暫時，真係暫時，休息，<span style=\"color: red;\">上演幾場和平散場既集會/遊行</span>，但低EQ黑察係唔會忍得住，要俾更多市民(尤其淺黃/淺藍/中間派)見到，爭取更多民意，令我地日後抗爭出師有名!!! 歷史上每場戰爭出師有名係好重要，你睇美國打伊打克都要話佢有核武就係咁解，<span style=\"color: red;\">任何運動中間派都係影響成敗既關鍵</span>!!! <br />\nb) 但係!!! 唔係叫你地呢段時間咩都唔做，反而呢段時間係最重要!!! <span style=\"color: red;\">你地要鍛練體能，有肥狗有瘦狗，但速龍係警隊既精銳部隊!!! 唔夠強就落得走唔切被打被捕既下場</span>，我地唔係要 <br />\n用血同人頭搶fo!!! &quot;<span style=\"color: green;\">不流血，不受傷，不被捕</span>&quot; 係因為我地珍惜每一位願意企出黎既手足!!! 我地真係唔可以再失去啦!!! <span style=\"color: green;\">鍛練體能，自律休息，整理裝備，先可以成為殺龍巴絲!!!</span> <br />\nc) <span style=\"color: red;\">不死守不強攻，要令黑警難清場難拉人難發泄，從心理擊潰佢地!!!</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拉唔到人=失敗=冇得紮， 但上頭又俾壓力，諗諗跑數既sales<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大丈夫就要做到能屈能伸，休息係為左走更遠既路!!!</span></span>  <br />\n唔使怕運動會冷卻，因為和理非會上場!!!<br />\n<br />\n4. 關於集會/遊行<br />\n每星期都要做，話俾全世界知我地既目標冇變過!!! 五大訴求，缺一不可!!!<br />\n韓國都行左20個星期先令到朴槿惠下台，<span style=\"color: red;\">政治改變非一朝一日之事，我地要展示抗爭既 <br />\n決心!!!</span> 個個星期都出係會好消粍民意，尤其香港人善忘... 呢樣就需要文宣手足努力!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我另外寫左篇關於文宣既，跪求參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各區開緊波，文宣手足同我入黎!!!!!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/acwCwOV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/acwCwOV</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 關於民間記者會<br />\n呢場運動可貴之處就係無大台，但亦因為無大台，難以抗衡政府媒體既一言堂，所有討論流於網上/散亂於民間，如果可以<span style=\"color: red;\">凝聚聲音作出有力反擊</span>，何不一試? 我地要有進步，要俾世界睇到我地既能力。要避免變成大台，可參考集會論壇/收集意見等方式，成為一個向世界發聲既平台。我地唔想被代表，所以更加要發聲，示範俾政府睇咩叫記者會。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申: 我同民間記者會冇任何關係，但今日睇完覺得真心滾動，大大力摑左班錄音機一巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但願有一天，我地可以除底口罩相見。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人加油!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n參考過以下手足既po<br />\n<br />\n今日三罷 無疑係失敗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417352</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭講既野係我地要改善既位，要留心聽<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1410958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1410958</a><br />\n<br />\n返緊intern，上一輩同事咁樣評價罷工同不合作運動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dxObJS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dxObJS</a><br />\n<br />\n警隊臨床心理學家指警察對示威口號產生幻聽、躁鬱<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1405473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1405473</a><br />\n<br />\n非常危險時期 抗爭者怒氣已經去到臨界點<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1409390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1409390</a><br />\n<br />\n其實林鄭哩步旗好精明<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1411312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1411312</a><br />\n<br />\n【BE WATER】大家知唔知係乜野意思？？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1397492\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1397492</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:43:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"975dbd7dc88d45a8903bdcf6ed712c24e0cd3f7a","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"313c12e6cbb689f166edff6c78abc98c6ae93b8c","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:53:29.000Z","msg":"回應返樓主個message：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不合作運動: </span></strong>要對返工既人客氣有禮，佢地或者會被感動，但係粗聲粗氣一定唔work,反而失民心（大忌）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">罷工：</span></strong>唔可以成日攪，７７７尋日個記招就係拎番出黎想我地群眾鬥群眾，要等時機同埋真係有topic <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武: </span></strong>佢係我地既皇牌，就因為佢地愈來愈重要，所以常用數一定要減少，可以保留實力，避免送頭，仲有俾時間佢地去唔同地方踩線搵新野。（有傳話佢地目標係８月底前捉最少７００個）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">集會/遊行：</span></strong>依家開始要小心，鬼肯定會多，同埋鄉事派同其他界別用返１４年雨革一樣（如的士佬，小巴佬等）黎打散我地，呢度要盡快踱對策。<br />\n<br />\n上面俾左Ｄ建議，望拋磚引玉。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"中間派好受道德感召，抗爭者對市民一定要有禮貌<br />\n<br />\n香港好難做到無限期罷工，除非警察打死市民&hellip;&hellip; 現階段可以考慮每隔星期一，升級就每星期一，始終唔係個個市民有能力持續罷，同埋罷工要加埋罷課先最有效<br />\n<br />\n勇武非常重要，所以一定要能屈能伸，暫時休息整裝待發，一個都不能再少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(唔係散水，係俾時間同能量煲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n集會/遊行愈多人愈安全，愈凝聚到力量，所以唔建議分散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />集思廣益呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4925f0d678b9d555de03af76818a4b9dcbb3f8f9","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"258c3c6c19c3074d4dcdd51112b32e71a9f9ba4b","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5453197bb53e4a3a2df0946554a589336695d11","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fedd4027187e9f0a4f19470c1e4d0634a964b8b8","tid":1424960,"uid":298802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"因為要陪養莊腳 迎接出年立法會選舉<br />\n只要立法會超過四十席 到時真的可以光復香港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:57:48.000Z","msg":"係，建制已經做緊野，但甦醒的香港人都唔想投俾政棍<br />\n我地又掛住打狗，冇時間精力討論<br />\n但有功能組別就冇可能超過四十席"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T21:56:15.000Z","msg":"要睇下文宣個邊有冇計，<br />\n又或者真係要搵Ｄ有選舉經驗既團體，睇下可唔可以協調一下出選，避免鬼打鬼。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:47:53.000Z","msg":"但今次運動冇大台就係怕俾政棍收割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未諗到點拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8714f2359bb2a5db1e8912e0c437dd58b35643","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"258c3c6c19c3074d4dcdd51112b32e71a9f9ba4b","tid":1424960,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5453197bb53e4a3a2df0946554a589336695d11","tid":1424960,"uid":297107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fedd4027187e9f0a4f19470c1e4d0634a964b8b8","tid":1424960,"uid":298802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:35:35.000Z","msg":"因為要陪養莊腳 迎接